Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:11.01,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I worked up my courage and tried turning around.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.81,0:00:14.10,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,By coincidence, Azuki turned around at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.60,0:00:17.14,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,A tenth of a second felt like ten seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.72,0:00:20.41,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Then I turned back and hurried onwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.56,0:00:26.03,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,100)}But I turned back again for two or three seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.08,0:00:33.78,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}In the distance, Azuki was looking back too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.67,0:00:43.41,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}It was like Azuki and I were on the same wavelength.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.87,0:02:13.19,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Wavelength?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.23,0:02:17.55,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Azuki probably turned around ten times, two of them just happened to meet with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.86,0:02:19.34,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.34,0:02:21.03,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,That must be an awesome feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.03,0:02:22.47,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something that I can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.47,0:02:23.90,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Are you making fun of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.90,0:02:25.42,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.40,0:02:30.52,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,The first time I saw Azuki was in my sixth year of elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.52,0:02:33.57,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}You and I went to Ake elementary and she went to Akeni elementary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.97,0:02:38.52,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,It was at a swimming contest between our schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.52,0:02:41.85,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,While she was on the other side of the pool, supporting, we watched each other the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.48,0:02:46.17,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, neither of us felt embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.90,0:02:50.61,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Also, at the middle school entrance ceremony,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.59,0:02:53.50,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,our eyes met again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.27,0:03:02.74,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, we were pretty close to each other so both of us turned away quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.81,0:03:04.88,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.88,0:03:07.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You were conscious of each other since elementary school?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:08.87,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,And you liked each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:12.81,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,But it's really only looking back now that I realize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.81,0:03:14.62,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, okay, but no matter how much your wavelengths match,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.62,0:03:17.24,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,if you don't exchange email addresses, you can't have a conversation with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.24,0:03:19.55,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine as long as I get her email by graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.17,0:03:21.51,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,For now, it's manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.11,0:03:23.12,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.41,0:03:24.56,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Here, I wrote five pages so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.56,0:03:25.34,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,That was fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.34,0:03:28.00,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I was writing while you were reminiscing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:32.18,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Futatsu no Chikyuu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:32.18,TL Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,TL note: Futatsu no Chikyuu = The Two Earths
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:39.12,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,The Earth we live on is nothing but a clone of the real Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:43.72,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,and we humans are nothing but clones of the humans on the real Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.05,0:03:48.36,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}Yes, we were made by the "real humans" as materials for experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.10,0:03:53.55,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,By being in the same environment, we are left independent and observed by our copies
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.55,0:03:56.07,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,in order to create a better world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.22,0:04:03.89,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,So, for the real Earth, researching us has brought an end to war and global warming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.63,0:04:07.51,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Shuujin...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.51,0:04:08.48,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,What did you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.11,0:04:10.70,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it, it sucks, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.88,0:04:13.41,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I knew a name was too high a hurdle to try to overcome so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.41,0:04:15.52,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know how to divide the panels and stuff, and the pictures...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:18.69,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Did you rip this story off from somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:21.89,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't, but forgive me if it has something in common with something else...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.18,0:04:24.59,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone could come up with something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.59,0:04:26.60,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't something anyone could come up with!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:28.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,At least I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.55,0:04:32.01,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'm really getting drawn in by this setup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.01,0:04:32.58,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:33.55,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.55,0:04:38.08,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,But after that part, all I had was the people from the real Earth fighting with these humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.08,0:04:39.86,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm attracted by it because I can picture that happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:42.79,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,It could be an all out battle, couldn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.79,0:04:45.45,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you have anything more interesting than this in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.74,0:04:46.60,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.82,0:04:49.20,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I had an idea for a sports story.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:50.35,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.95,0:04:52.64,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,One called {\i1}Gurasan Pitcher{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.95,0:04:52.64,TL Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,TL note: Gurasan Pitcher = Sunglasses Pitcher
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.99,0:04:57.00,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,An elementary schooler with a strong fast ball is trying to make it to the pros,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.00,0:04:58.95,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,700)}but he gets hit right in the forehead by a shot hit towards the pitcher, and is blinded.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:05.25,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Ten years later, suddenly a pitcher wearing sunglasses appears on a pro mound.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.25,0:05:09.70,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,With 180 km/h throws at every angle; high, low, inside, and outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:11.61,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,he pitches a perfect game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:16.36,Main,Sunglasses,0000,0000,0000,,Having never given up on his dream of going pro,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.36,0:05:20.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,there's a story of the secret special training he did for ten years with his dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.92,0:05:16.46,Main UP,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Next, 38. {Overlapping with Shuujin}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:17.29,Main UP,Sunglasses,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.53,0:05:20.86,Main UP,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Sunglasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:21.85,Main,Sunglasses,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.10,0:05:25.65,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that he can't see gets out, and while he's in a dispute with the baseball association,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:28.64,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,he battles with rivals trying to hit his throws.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:31.56,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you had talent, Shuujin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:34.14,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Normally nobody could come up with that much of a story on that premise!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.38,0:05:37.07,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,S–Seriously? You really think I have talent?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:38.97,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, usually it'd sound stu—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.37,0:05:39.65,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:42.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I've been trying desperately to come up with stories day after day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.31,0:05:45.38,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Even I thought I might've been over confident...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.11,0:05:49.83,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,But now that you've recognized me, I've really got confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.33,0:05:51.51,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.51,0:05:53.11,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.11,0:05:54.46,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.46,0:05:56.61,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I'll draw artwork that can compliment your story.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.21,0:06:01.32,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,So which story should we go with?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:02.98,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Futatsu no Chikyuu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.98,0:06:05.30,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a feeling {\i1}Gurasan{\i0} isn't suited to being a series.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:05.75,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.60,0:06:08.38,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Is there an ideal amount of pages it should be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.38,0:06:12.55,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the Rookie Award has set 31 to 45 pages.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.82,0:06:14.77,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.44,0:06:18.00,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Well, don't worry about the page count for now, just draw a whole lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:18.66,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.21,0:06:23.91,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.96,0:06:30.16,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,That was fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:32.64,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I already had the beginning in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.50,0:06:37.30,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, even if it's done at a fast pace, it doesn't matter if it's not interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:44.33,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Saikou?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.08,0:06:46.19,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.31,0:06:48.20,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.81,0:06:51.03,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Takagi, come here a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.73,0:06:52.85,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,She's calling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:54.44,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.44,0:06:55.79,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, she's coming over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.79,0:06:56.30,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.61,0:06:58.42,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Ignoring people when they call you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:01.39,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,She seems kinda angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.39,0:07:02.72,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Ignore her, ignore her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.53,0:07:05.67,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Takagi, I've got something to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.79,0:07:08.04,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:11.20,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:16.93,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Miho said, "Why does Takagi-kun know about my dreams for the future?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.93,0:07:18.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,"You told him, didn't you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.28,0:07:19.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she got angry at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.31,0:07:21.91,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't really matter, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.91,0:07:24.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I just checked with her to see if it was true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:27.13,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,And I told this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:28.67,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's my friend Mashiro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:30.03,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:34.10,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,I told you Miho's shy and that you shouldn't tell anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:37.24,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I won't tell anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.24,0:07:41.41,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,How about you ask her how she's gonna be a seiyuu if she's that shy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.41,0:07:43.48,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell I could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:47.01,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I won't spread it around anymore so relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.01,0:07:49.26,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,So, did you get rejected by Miho?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.87,0:07:51.16,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.16,0:07:52.79,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,You said you talked with Miho, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:56.26,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying I just asked her to see if it was true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.82,0:07:59.26,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Azuki likes someone else anyway, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:00.74,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.90,0:08:01.53,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:06.50,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, but third year middle school girls usually have someone they like, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:08.41,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.41,0:08:10.93,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But Miho never said anything about that, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.45,0:08:14.79,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait a second, why were you probing me about Miho anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.98,0:08:18.86,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Well, that's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.86,0:08:20.81,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to talk to you, Miyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:26.49,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,L–Let me think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:30.43,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,H–Hang on Miyoshi... san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.55,0:08:32.30,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, now you've done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.89,0:08:37.28,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,If you say you were joking, she'll either cry or get pissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:41.76,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,You know her, she's been in nationals for karate or aikido or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:45.93,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Also, she likes you in the first place, doesn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.93,0:08:47.02,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.02,0:08:48.94,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, she told you her best friend's secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.94,0:08:50.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems she likes you, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:52.69,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Then, she said, "Let me think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.69,0:08:54.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way she would say that if she didn't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:56.26,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:57.68,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't let it go on like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:09:00.20,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,She's not bad, that Miyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:02.40,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.40,0:09:03.44,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.44,0:09:06.41,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,She's Azuki's best friend, so she must be a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.79,0:09:08.88,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,What is it Kaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:10.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted to talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.31,0:09:11.90,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Takagi hit on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:12.79,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.79,0:09:13.35,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:16.12,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of him, Takagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.12,0:09:19.40,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's good at studying and exercise, and he's tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.40,0:09:20.71,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.71,0:09:22.34,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not good enough for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.34,0:09:23.67,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.67,0:09:24.80,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,You're cute, Kaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.63,0:09:27.61,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Takagi-kun thinks so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.12,0:09:30.71,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.71,0:09:31.46,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.20,0:09:34.93,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,Kaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:39.31,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,But Takagi can definitely get Iwase to go out with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.31,0:09:41.08,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,It's even a rumor in our class.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:45.51,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think Iwase-san is someone easy for boys to approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.51,0:09:48.74,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,"Boys are stupid, hmhm." That sort of feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.74,0:09:50.25,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not that far...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.25,0:09:51.50,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:54.23,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the person you like, Miho?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.48,0:09:56.54,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:09:58.84,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.92,0:10:00.00,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Like I was saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.00,0:10:04.32,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, hurry up and tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.32,0:10:05.86,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't anybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.43,0:10:11.66,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,You're kinda stuck up, just like Iwase.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.52,0:10:14.91,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen you talking with a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.91,0:10:16.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's stuck up, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:18.73,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,Kaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.73,0:10:19.32,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.32,0:10:21.61,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just embarrassed around boys so I can't talk to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:24.53,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,I really like boys, even more than you, Kaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.53,0:10:24.96,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.29,0:10:28.14,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's because I don't have any brothers,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:29.49,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,but I get really self-conscious
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.49,0:10:32.09,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,and go bright red from just trying to talk to them, so I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.09,0:10:32.81,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.33,0:10:38.43,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,It's really funny when you start talking like a teacher, Miho.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.43,0:10:39.25,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.25,0:10:42.78,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,But when you do, you're always serious so I know you're not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.25,0:10:44.33,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,Kaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:49.47,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,When you give Takagi-kun your reply, do it alone, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.33,0:10:51.76,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,I hate being around for those sorts of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.72,0:10:55.07,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Takagi and Mashiro are back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.30,0:10:57.05,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,W–What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.45,0:10:58.40,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.19,0:11:00.37,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Miho...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:08.62,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we're on the same wavelength.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.62,0:11:11.04,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Miyoshi was just turning around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.28,0:11:14.64,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,"Was just..."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.37,0:11:23.69,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.76,0:11:24.86,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.65,0:11:27.92,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times I write it, I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.92,0:11:29.82,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,And it'll be summer vacation soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.30,0:11:31.92,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:34.66,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still not at the level where I can do a manuscript.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:39.72,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Worst case scenario, you can write the second half while I'm drawing the first half.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:41.85,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.24,0:11:44.17,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Sixth?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.17,0:11:45.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.19,0:11:47.46,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Sixth in the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.46,0:11:50.54,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,The test had the same pattern of questions you said it'd have.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:51.00,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.24,0:11:52.14,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Now we just...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:52.64,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Ah—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:03.06,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,W–Wavelengths...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.05,0:12:07.91,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I know your dad said it was okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.52,0:12:11.01,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,but to stay stuffed in a workplace all vacation long...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:13.40,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,As your mother I need to put my foot down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:23.76,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Please try to come home once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.76,0:12:24.32,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.81,0:12:28.00,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Saikou.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.00,0:12:29.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me stay here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:33.33,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine with me, but didn't your parents make a big fuss about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.33,0:12:34.18,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,They were pretty cool with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.77,0:12:36.19,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.37,0:12:39.22,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,He used to work hard and drink those, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.22,0:12:40.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawaguchi Tarou-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.54,0:12:43.31,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're gonna be working hard too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.77,0:12:46.05,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are trying to follow his footsteps.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.75,0:12:48.86,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Then let me revise my statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:52.03,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Let's finish the manuscript before the end of summer vacation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.03,0:12:52.82,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.81,0:12:57.04,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Bitter...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.87,0:12:59.13,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:01.28,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,My name is becoming a manga! {Nothing written is legible}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.28,0:13:02.96,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,This is a name, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.96,0:13:04.66,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fixing the panel division and composition.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:08.42,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, even this looks like it'd make an amazing manga if it were inked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:10.76,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,It's still a long way off from completion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:12.99,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Next I've got the under-sketch to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.99,0:13:14.67,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be doing the inking any time soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:16.29,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:17.51,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,It's not at that stage yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:21.51,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to improve my level right up until I do the inking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.04,0:13:24.91,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Saikou, even though you say manga doesn't have a limit,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.91,0:13:26.06,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,aren't your standards a little too high?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.60,0:13:27.72,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,From my perspective, this is plenty. {qc}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.72,0:13:29.36,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm still not there at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:35.32,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, do it the way you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.32,0:13:37.70,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll keep doing the name until it's something I approve of.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.03,0:13:42.82,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I won't interfere with your name, and you won't interfere with my drawings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.49,0:13:44.34,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:44.80,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.96,0:14:00.60,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Saikou, are you asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.60,0:14:02.46,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,As if I could get to sleep that fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:04.41,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.41,0:14:06.65,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking too much, so it's actually making it hard to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.05,0:14:08.77,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to read some more manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.37,0:14:11.11,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are good...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.38,0:14:14.57,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Are there any manga you've been into recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.57,0:14:17.65,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Hm, it's got to be "Dragon Ball."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:21.03,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,That's your favorite manga, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.03,0:14:23.94,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of unshakable, and it's kind of my starting point.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.82,0:14:27.28,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, did you ever make-believe Dragon Ball when you were a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:28.09,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:31.34,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Fusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:36.48,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Shuujin, your {\i1}sion{\i0} timing was late, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.48,0:14:40.70,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,My {\i1}sion{\i0} was perfect, your {\i1}sion{\i0} was too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:43.82,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,No, you need to say {\i1}sion{\i0} with more of a {\i1}SION!{\i0} kind of feeling,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:45.05,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,or it's not a real {\i1}sion{\i0} !
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:47.78,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying my {\i1}jan{\i0} wasn't the real thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.48,0:14:49.46,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Who's {\i1}Jan{\i0} ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.67,0:14:51.78,Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Eh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.78,0:14:53.83,Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:15:01.83,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Saikou, you're awake too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:03.82,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Shuujin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:06.83,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to try inking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.56,0:15:10.77,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,There's only a month left of summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.77,0:15:13.00,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still not fully satisfied with my pen handling,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.02,0:15:15.45,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,but as I expected, I must get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:18.75,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not saying you should rush the name though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:21.52,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,You stick to doing it until you're satisfied with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:22.16,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.44,0:15:54.91,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I've finished up to the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.91,0:15:56.74,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, take a little break.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.27,0:15:59.48,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you should too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.48,0:16:00.05,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.11,0:16:05.14,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:07.14,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Hm... Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.20,0:16:23.40,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, now I've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.40,0:16:25.33,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I can fix this with white-out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.35,0:16:27.47,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna go outside for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.72,0:16:30.65,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.99,0:16:34.16,Main UP,Person,0000,0000,0000,,The top hit on the charts this week,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.16,0:16:37.90,Main UP,Person,0000,0000,0000,,though it was only released in July, has already achieved one million in sales.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.90,0:16:39.65,Main UP,,0000,0000,0000,,KOOGY's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:43.35,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.34,0:16:46.09,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.09,0:16:48.40,Main,Girl A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this song sure is good, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.66,0:16:50.35,Main,Girl B,0000,0000,0000,,It's KOOGY, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.35,0:16:52.07,Main,Girl B,0000,0000,0000,,That song from his new album.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:54.52,Main,Girl A,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go to his summer tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.52,0:16:57.03,Main,Girl B,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you've got to enjoy your summer vacation!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.41,0:16:58.19,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Shuujin?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.93,0:17:03.04,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go back and work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:03.57,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.90,0:17:11.41,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time for me to get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.32,0:17:15.11,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Saikou?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.70,0:17:26.47,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,He's already done all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:00.08,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I sure kept you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.32,0:18:02.48,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to the convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.48,0:18:04.10,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Rest for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:05.54,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,If we need to buy anything, I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.42,0:18:10.00,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,From this point on, I won't be touching the manuscript, so I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.96,0:18:11.80,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.21,0:18:17.49,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, maybe Azuki will come if we call her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:22.00,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,"Master, your meal is ready."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.00,0:18:22.83,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.43,0:18:27.11,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kidding, I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.11,0:18:29.18,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought it'd get you energized.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.18,0:18:30.32,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,You liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.32,0:18:33.20,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I know Azuki's not that kind of girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.77,0:18:44.18,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, I'm trying to take this book.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.41,0:18:48.89,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.01,0:18:58.33,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,You sure took a while, were there no convenience stores open nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.08,0:19:01.02,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.02,0:19:01.90,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is from the same place as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.32,0:19:05.37,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you bought a {\i1}Jack{\i0} for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:06.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.20,0:19:12.50,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Niizuma Eiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.79,0:19:20.51,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Eiji's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:22.76,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just the drawings, the story's interesting too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.60,0:19:24.77,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,As we are now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.41,0:19:28.07,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,If we're losing... it's with the pictures!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.09,0:19:34.10,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,S–Saikou!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.13,0:19:36.22,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.22,0:19:37.35,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I don't either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.89,0:19:40.08,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,But even the story was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.08,0:19:41.11,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way in hell I'll lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.74,0:19:45.39,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything I can do to help out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.84,0:19:48.41,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,You finished your name alone, Shuujin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.26,0:19:50.78,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I want to finish my job alone, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.18,0:20:44.25,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,All right, white-out is done!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.28,0:20:47.58,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Now just for...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.58,0:20:49.66,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Saikou, let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.66,0:20:51.68,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't interfere with your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.68,0:20:53.40,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,You won't interfere with my artwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.67,0:20:58.43,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just thought this way we'd both be working on it at the moment it was finished...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.92,0:21:03.33,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Can you attach the tones?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.33,0:21:03.84,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.52,0:21:07.95,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Here, attach these to all of the Earth soldier's pants!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.95,0:21:09.54,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.88,0:21:12.98,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep going nonstop until we're done!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.98,0:21:13.70,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.30,0:21:33.32,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,The drawings are good, but I don't about my story.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.32,0:21:36.05,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,The story is good, but I dunno about my drawings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.62,0:21:41.52,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Saikou.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.52,0:21:42.18,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.22,0:21:48.59,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.59,0:21:50.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think this sort of thing is embarrassing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.43,0:21:57.51,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Saikou.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.58,0:22:07.81,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's call right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.81,0:22:09.84,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,The number is probably stored in the phone's memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.84,0:22:12.91,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think if we call this way, they'll think it's Kawaguchi Tarou's ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.91,0:22:14.52,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,No one will remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.52,0:22:16.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Call on your cell phone if you're that worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.95,0:22:19.93,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,What should I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.32,0:22:23.35,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Just something like "I'd like to bring in a manuscript."
